http://daeso.uvt.nl
e.marsi@gmail.com



--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

DAESO Dutch is a Python library developed in the DAESO (Detecting And
Exploiting Semantic Overlap) research project. It provides support for working
with Dutch parallel corpora using the Alpino parser. It also contains support
for running graph alignment experiments on the DAESO corpus, and for building
automatic graph aligners.


